com.camerontec.catalys.util.collection

Class SmallIntMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<Integer,Object>
      • com.camerontec.catalys.util.collection.SmallIntMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Map<Integer,Object>

    public class SmallIntMap
extends AbstractMap<Integer,Object>
implements Serializable
    Map optimized for small positive integer keys.

    Note that this is an efficient map for all integers, not just small positive ones, but it works fastest for small positive integers. It can be used for a mixture of integers, small and large.
